    "The Multifidelity Max-Value Entropy Search (MFMES) acquisition function can be formulated extending the maxvalue entropy search to a multifidelity setting as follows [130]:(27) 3 (x, l) = n l ∏ i=1 1 -R x, x (l) i.",
